query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on q.site_id = s.site_id AND tq.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on t.site_id = s.site_id AND tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.name IN ('asp.net-identity',
'google-maps-markers',
'internet-explorer-8');
